x1 = eq.Variable(1)
x2 = eq.Variable(2)
def compute(variables, g, h):
    x1, x2 = hj.HyperJet.variables(variables)
    f = x1 ** 2 + x1 * x2 + x2 ** 3
    return explode(f, g, h)
element = eq.LambdaObjective([x1, x2], compute)
g = np.empty(2)
h = np.empty((2, 2))
f = element.compute(g, h)
assert_equal(f, 11)
assert_equal(g, [4, 13])
assert_equal(h, [[2, 1], [1, 12]])
